{"tid":2404273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奈雪的茶遞交上市申請　去年首3季虧損2751萬元","createTime":"2021-02-11T15:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T16:28:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"20950a73113b538b07b730822d7cceb58161b115","tid":2404273,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575367-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575367-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=419f2ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575367-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fbeb37c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575367-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n奈雪的茶向聯交所遞交的上市申請，由摩根大通、招銀國際及華泰國際擔任保薦人。<br />\n<br />\n根據初步招股文件顯示，去年首3季虧損2751萬元人民幣，虧損按年擴大6.1倍。期內，收入21.1億元，按年升20.8%。<br />\n<br />\n公司計劃，今明兩年主要在一線城市及新一線城市，分別開設約300間及350間「奈雪的茶」品牌的茶飲店。至去年9月底，「奈雪的茶」茶飲店共422間，當中，香港及日本各有1間店。<br />\n<br />\n文件顯示，上市集資將用於未來3年擴張茶飲店網絡，並提高市場滲透率；開展整體營運數碼化，以提升營運效率；提升供應鏈能力，以支持規模擴張；用作營運資金及一般企業用途。"},{"pid":"137401e46297aa0c31e14f598a2f5380fb286460","tid":2404273,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"係咪另一隻瑞幸咖啡?"},{"pid":"2105caa8ea01d9a2ab82af3c71abe0c70066b433","tid":2404273,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"業務越蝕，隻股越升得勁"},{"pid":"ff414da24996898e386b8e623d00d8a6d5ad91e4","tid":2404273,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"137401e46297aa0c31e14f598a2f5380fb286460","tid":2404273,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"係咪另一隻瑞幸咖啡?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"奈雪的茶为国内知名茶饮品牌，创立于2015年，总部